WEBVTT

00:00:00.920 --> 00:00:05.126
Rodil sem se in odraščal v Sierri Leone,

00:00:05.126 --> 00:00:07.371
v majhni in čudoviti državi

00:00:07.371 --> 00:00:09.076
v Zahodni Afriki,

00:00:09.076 --> 00:00:11.980
v državi, bogati tako z materialnimi viri

00:00:11.980 --> 00:00:14.312
kot s kreativnim talentom.

00:00:14.312 --> 00:00:16.274
Vendar pa je Sierra Leone razvpita

00:00:16.274 --> 00:00:18.688
zavoljo desetletne 
uporniške vojne v 90-ih,

00:00:18.688 --> 00:00:21.778
ko so bile celotne vasi požgane.

00:00:21.778 --> 00:00:25.990
Po ocenah so 8000-im možem,
ženam in otrokom

00:00:25.990 --> 00:00:30.256
v tem času amputirali roke ali noge.